Package org.keyboardplaying.mapper.parser

The objects in charge of converting the string values in map from and to the object fields.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ElaborateParser<F>
    This interface is to be used when the SimpleParser does not allow for sufficient functionality (e.g.
    SimpleParser<T>
    Implementations of this interface are to be used to switch from object to String.
    TemporalParser<T>
    Specific version of SimpleParser for temporal objects.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseTemporalParser<T>
    This implementation of SimpleParser provides some utility methods when parsing time representations.
    BigIntegerParser
    Implementation of SimpleParser for BigInteger to String parsing.
    BooleanParser
    Implementation of SimpleParser for Boolean to String parsing.
    CalendarParser
    Implementation of SimpleParser for Calendar to String parsing.
    DateParser
    Implementation of SimpleParser for Date to String parsing.
    ElaborateParser.None
    An ElaborateParser when the SimpleParser should be used.
    IntegerParser
    Implementation of SimpleParser for Integer to String parsing.
    LongParser
    Implementation of SimpleParser for Long to String parsing.
    StringParser
    Implementation of SimpleParser for String to String parsing.
